    <h1>HTTPS</h1>
    <p class="description">The encrypted version of HTTP that protects data between browser and server. A confirmed Google ranking signal since 2014, required for modern browser features, and the baseline for user trust on any website.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
